1. On *odbija* da prizna svoju grešku. (He refuses to admit his mistake.)
2. Moj zahtev je *odbijen*. (My request was rejected.)
3. Oni su *odbili* ponudu za posao. (They turned down the job offer.)
4. Kada je čula vest, ona je *odbila* da veruje. (When she heard the news, she refused to believe it.)
5. Advokat je *odbio* da komentariše slučaj. (The lawyer declined to comment on the case.)
6. Kompanija je *odbila* da plati kaznu. (The company refused to pay the fine.)
7. On *odbija* da sarađuje s drugim ljudima. (He refuses to collaborate with other people.)
8. Njegova ljubav prema njoj *odbija* da umre. (His love for her refuses to die.)
9. Odbijanje poziva za proslavu nije uvek loše. (Refusing an invitation to a party is not always bad.)
10. Učenik je *odbio* da preda svoj mobilni telefon nastavniku. (The student refused to hand over his mobile phone to the teacher.)